The '''Bon Secours Health System''' is the largest private [[hospital network]] in [[Republic of Ireland|Ireland]].<ref>http://www.advertiser.ie/galway/article/28089</ref> It is owned by the [[Roman Catholic]] [[Bon Secours Sisters]]<ref>http://www.bonsecoursireland.org/index.cfm/page/aboutus</ref> and consists of: * [[Bon Secours Hospital, Cork]] * [[Bon Secours Hospital, Dublin]] * [[Bon Secours Hospital, Galway]] * [[Barringtons Hospital, Limerick]] * [[Bon Secours Hospital, Tralee]]
